name: Condor 767-300ER "Ja zu FRA" livery takeoff from Calgary
description:
This video is dedicated to Fraport Spotter, who spots at Frankfurt and has an excellent channel with many great videos, so please check him out!
http://www.youtube.com/user/thefraspotter

Hello everyone, this is a Condor Flugdienst Boeing 767-300ER departing Calgary International Airport, bound for Frankfurt-Main. This was my first time seeing Condor, so it was pretty nice to catch. Love those winglets on the 763!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
